summary: I’m on “The Rise of the Cybermen,” and I noticed that Ten keeps putting on glasses to read things, which doesn’t make sense to...
body:
I’m on “The Rise of the Cybermen,” and I noticed that Ten keeps putting on glasses to read things, which doesn’t make sense to me since Nine never did that. So all I can think is either

a. This regeneration has bad eyesight and he decided at some point to get glasses

b. David Tennant has bad eyesight and decided to wear his own on camera when he needed them

c. The Doctor realizes he looks hot in glasses, or

d. Any combination of the above three
